<plot>A simple game of catch between Kevin &amp; his son, Alex, turns dangerous when Alex's favorite ball is lost down a deep embankment. When Kevin returns later that night to find the ball, he comes face to face with a sinister killer that has ensnared all who cross its path. The Ball is a terrifying account of the lengths a father will go to fight for his son's most prized possession.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?541761</url></doc>
